author: donaldp
msg: Removed preAdd method as it is assumed that only valid Entrys will be added.
Removed the ability for subclasses to provide alternate ApplicationFrame as that is a flexability not really needed.

author: donaldp
msg: Updates BlockDAG to work with BlockMetaData rather than BlockEntrys.
Alter interface so that it returns the path instead of taking a Visitor. Now it will be the responsibility of caller to execute visitor on element in path.
The above changes also allowed the complexity of DAG to be reduced by removing i18n/logging factors.
